question.title: Error while applying OWSM policies on Web service created from Jdeveloper 11g (SEVERE: java.io.FileNotFoundException: .\config\jps-config.xml)

node.contents: I created sample class Testws with one simple method sayHi(String name) that simply showing welcome message. The target is to create web service application for this class and applying OWSM policies.
